{"tid":1274120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佢地係一班為左香港可以奉獻自己嘅人","createTime":"2019-07-01T15:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T15:42:38.000Z","uid":19255,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2839e838668d038475a13092771176807f1991f","tid":1274120,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:42:38.000Z","msg":"佢地好清楚留低好大機會要坐10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都有自己嘅包袱，但佢地為左香港可以付出佢地自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以話佢地傻，但係佢哋只係單純咁愛香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n偏偏佢地係人地口中嘅暴徒，要比人打，俾人拉去坐監，明明佢地先係最愛香港嘅市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔想見到佢哋送死，不過尊重佢地嘅決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}